Here's everything you need:

### 1. Detect the current system theme

```csharp
AppTheme current = Application.Current!.RequestedTheme;
// AppTheme.Light, AppTheme.Dark, or AppTheme.Unspecified
```

### 2. Subscribe to real-time theme changes

```csharp
// In your App constructor or startup code:
Application.Current!.RequestedThemeChanged += (s, e) =>
{
    Debug.WriteLine($"Theme changed to: {e.RequestedTheme}");

    // Optionally swap full ResourceDictionaries:
    ApplyTheme(e.RequestedTheme == AppTheme.Dark
        ? new DarkTheme()
        : new LightTheme());
};
```

### 3. Force a specific theme (ignoring system setting)

```csharp
// Force dark mode
Application.Current!.UserAppTheme = AppTheme.Dark;

// Reset to follow system
Application.Current!.UserAppTheme = AppTheme.Unspecified;
```

Persist the user's choice with `Preferences`:

```csharp
// Save
Preferences.Set("AppTheme", "Dark");

// Restore on startup
Application.Current!.UserAppTheme = Preferences.Get("AppTheme", "System") switch
{
    "Light" => AppTheme.Light,
    "Dark"  => AppTheme.Dark,
    _       => AppTheme.Unspecified
};
```

### ⚠️ Critical: Android requires `ConfigChanges.UiMode`

Without this, theme toggles cause a full activity restart instead of firing the event:

```csharp
[Activity(ConfigurationChanges = ConfigChanges.ScreenSize
                               | ConfigChanges.Orientation
                               | ConfigChanges.UiMode  // ← required
                               | ConfigChanges.ScreenLayout
                               | ConfigChanges.SmallestScreenSize
                               | ConfigChanges.Density)]
public class MainActivity : MauiAppCompatActivity { }
```

### XAML: Use `AppThemeBinding` for automatic light/dark

```xml
<Label Text="Hello"
       TextColor="{AppThemeBinding Light=Green, Dark=Red}"
       BackgroundColor="{AppThemeBinding Light=White, Dark=Black}" />
```

If you're swapping `ResourceDictionary` themes at runtime, always bind with **`DynamicResource`** (not `StaticResource`) so values update live.
